room_title: Escape room "The Gallery" by Baltimaze Escape Rooms in Baltimore
review: Fun group experience The Gallery room is a tough one. Our party of four didn't make it out, however I'd do it again.

room_title: Escape room "The Gallery" by Baltimaze Escape Rooms in Baltimore
review: Escaped from 'The Gallery' on Baltimaze's Opening Day! Our team of 10 had an awesome time working together to get out with just over a minute left. I was so impressed at the complexity of the puzzles that the Baltimaze team had put together. It truly was a fun and unique experience, I can't wait to get back and try one of their other rooms out! Definitely worth checking out if you're in the area.
